cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.Distributed, cs.AR 

The paper discusses the design of a network layer that spans across multiple datacenters and cloud providers, which involves topics related to computer networks (cs.NI), distributed systems (cs.Distributed), and cloud computing (cs.DC). The proposed solution also requires coordination and control over the communications between different clouds, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper mentions the potential use of augmented reality (cs.AR) in the context of network visualization, although this is not a central aspect of the work.
